=== EVENT_SPATIAL_ANOMALY ===
# id: 26
# title: Spatial Anomaly
# chinese_title: 空间异常
# category: AnomalyEncounter
# mode: starmap

Space itself seems to bend ahead. Stars stretch into impossible shapes around a swirling distortion that your instruments cannot fully resolve.

* [Navigate through the anomaly]
  ~ lose_hull(8)
  穿过 (chuānguò) — pass through
* [Go around it (costs extra fuel)] {requires: fuel >= 5}
  ~ lose_fuel(5)
  绕行 (ràoxíng) — detour
* [Study it from a safe distance]
  ~ gain_radical("力")
  异常 (yìcháng) — anomaly
